Kotoba (page 2 of 3)
Say k!help CommandNameHere to see more information about a specific command.
k!examples (short: k!ex)
Search Jisho for example sentences. Example: k!examples 少し
k!translate (short: k!t)
Use Google Translate to translate text. Example: k!translate 吾輩は猫である
k!furigana (short: k!furi, k!f)
Render furigana for Japanese text. Example: k!furigana 吾輩は猫である
k!español (short: k!es)
Buscar Hispadic para resultados del diccionaro Español-Japonés.
k!yourei (short: k!y)
Search 用例.jp for more example sentences. Example: k!yourei 少し
k!anime (short: k!a)
Search Kitsu.io for anime information. Example: k!anime Monster
